<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694327>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 46. Female genitalia of Siberian Ennominae. A—M. continuaria; B—M. liturata; C—M. wauaria; D—M. circumflexaria; E, F—M. artesiaria; G—M. brunneata; H—M. loricaria; I—Chiasmia clathrata; J—Ch. saburraria; F— signum. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4694327/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694274>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 28. Male genitalia of Siberian Ennominae.A, B—Isturgia arenacearia; C–E—Narraga fasciolaria; F–H—Digrammia rippertaria; I–K—Macaria circumflexaria; L–N—M. wauaria. A, D, F, I, L—genital segment; B, E, G, J, M—phallos; C—valva; H, K, N—VIII abdominal sternite. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4694274/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694230>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 11. Adults of some Siberian Ennominae in live. A—Hypoxystis reticulata (female); B—Arichanna mandshuriaria (male); C—Jankowskia bituminaria (male); D—Synopsia strictaria (female); E—Phthonandria emaria (male); F—Macaria circumflexaria (male). Photos by Marya Dementyeva (Irkutsk)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4694230/files/figure.png" .

